#
# Bonjour (aka Rendezvous) enabled version of echo server/client
#

= Requirements =

To build and run this example, one must download and install bonjour Java
API from apple: http://developer.apple.com/darwin/projects/bonjour/
You must register with ADC in order to download the source code.

The Bonjour jar should be installed into JAVA_HOME/lib as well as the
native JNI libraries should be installed into the correct place.


= Running the Example =

To run the server type:

  ant run-server
  
To run the client type:

  ant run-client
  
You can run multiple servers to see that the client discovers all of
them.
